        "meta_description": "Simon and Sally from England connected with their ancestors in Shimla where they were born and buried. Several British descendants come to Shimla to retrace their roots and find graves or birth and death records of their ancestors who came to India to serve the British Empire and then never left.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
